by Li Yafei, deputy secretary general for Relations Across the
Taiwan Strait (ARATS), arrived here today on a seven-day visit to
Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
Li Yafei told the press at Taoyuan Airport that while in Taipei
he will meet with officials of the Straits Exchange Foundation
(SEF) to discuss and exchange views about SEF Chairman Koo
Chen-fu's upcoming trip to the mainland this fall.
</P>
