Procedural negotiations on holding political talks across
the Taiwan Straits should begin as early as possible, Li said.
</P>
<P>
Before this takes place, however, both sides can exchange views
through informal channels and increase their dialogue, he said.
</P>
<P>
The 24-member group includes the headmasters of several
Beijing primary and middle schools. It is in Taiwan at the
invitation of a Taiwan-based cultural and educational fund.
</P>
<P>
The mainland headmasters will visit schools in Taiwan and
exchange views on extracurricular education with local educators.
