state of Chiapas could be stopped through peaceful talks.
</P>
<P>
The Latin American countries should not only engage themselves
in economic development and regional integration but also attach
importance to the fight against such destabilizing factors as drug
trafficking, terrorism, corruption, violent crimes, Annan added.
