<HEADLINE> Philippine President Opens Exhibit, Book on ASEAN </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 24 (Xinhua)-- Philippine President Joseph Estrada
opened here Friday an exhibition showcasing projects in various
fields in the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN).
</P>
<P>
Estrada unveiled the exhibit on the occasion of the 31st ASEAN
Ministerial Meeting (AMM) in the presence of ASEAN foreign
ministers, senior officials, eminent personages and delegates.
</P>
